Javier Pereira (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Javier_Pereira_(actor) 0 Javier Pereira Collado (born 5 November 1981) is a Spanish actor. He won Goya Award for Best New Actor for his performance in Stockholm (2013) at the 28th Goya Awards. Javier_Pereira_Collado ( born_5_November_1981 ) is a_Spanish_actor . He won Goya_Award for_Best_New_Actor for his_performance in Stockholm_(_2013_) at the_28th_Goya_Awards .
